arabic.title: على ورق الفل
text: انا لا حيلتي ولا في ودني
يا ابو رمش جراح انا قلبي ارتاح على﻿ ايدك
عشان بحبك عاوزني ابوس على ايدك
انا لا حيلتي ولا في صدري
انا لا حيلتي ولا في رجلي

english.title: Ala warag el fol
text: On tha jasmine leaves pamper me
I can't bear all this begging
I told you let's sell them
and i'll spend the night with you
but this ring in my hand
I told you let's sell it
and i'll spend the night with you
On tha jasmine leaves pamper me
I told you let's sell it
And i'll spend the night with you
on the jasmine leaves pamper me
Oh you handsome wearing this costume
I want to repent because of you
You will put my heart at ease
is it because i love you
to kiss your hands means to beg you)
but this necklace around my neck
i told you let's sell it
and we will spend the night together
I told you let's sell it
And i'l lspend the night with you
On tha jasmine leaves pamper me
I can't bear all this begging

arabic.title: لأ والنبي يا عبده
text: الرجل تدب يا عبده مطرح ما تحب يا عبده
طلعت فوق .. فوق السطوح اشكي للهوا منك
واقوله علي علي جري واللي حصل منك
تهجر وتشمت عزالي والناس تتصعب علي حالي
أن كنت يا يا حليوة شاريني

english.title: Not by the prophet
text: One can set his/her foot anywhere he/she likes
I go up, up to the roof complaining my suffering from you to the air
I will tell him about you , about what happened and what you did
You abandoned me and you rubbed it In my face , people feel sorry for me
And this Is not over yet
One can set his or her foot anywhere he or she likes
Not even by the prophet Abduh
If you are gone, I'll ask about you
